nodes.text: The Killik Praetor was an oversized Killik that lived on Alderaan during the Cold War. It and its nest were used by the Sith Lord Nefarid to attack the Mensaav Laboratory, and the Jedi Master Orgus Din was forced to kill the crazed insectoid with his former student in the aftermath of the attack.
